    <string name="instructions">        This is just like normal chess, except that the board is warped around a central "singularity".\n
        Straight movements become curved around the singularity, and diagonal movements become distorted.\n 
        \n
        The only pieces impervious to the effects of the singularity are the pawns. Pawns follow straight forward trajectories right across the screen.\n
        \n
        No empassant is allowed.\n 
